Interface IStreamDecoder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, IDataDecoder, IFilteringDataStream, Iterable<Map<String,Object>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractStreamDecoder

    public interface IStreamDecoder
extends IDataDecoder
    This interface describes a data stream decoder, which adds additional methods to managing data via InputStreams.
